message.body: So how did singing at church go, white Etta James?
It was ok... Where'd Etta j come from?
Well you tweeted you didn't like people saying you sound like an angel, so I just picked a saucy black woman...don't read into that.
Hah. Got it.
Hey I don't know if you are busy but I'm headed to dinkytown so I can be around people, if you would like to join let me know.
I'm a working lady now, so I'm at my desk until 5 m-f
Oh okay
Sorry dude
It's cool no worries. Hope you enjoy work
Hey when you get off work you should come to 280 and have a beer with me...just sayin
Traffic is awful man. I'd have to do it later. We can plan something if you want to?
That's okay. No big deal
We can do something some other day.
Well....if you want to see a terribly messy room (cause I just don't care) and a drunk peter feel free to come over anytime
Totes the wrong person...I am an idiot......
And especially delightful
Are you just inviting anyone to your room while drunk? That's a recipe for disaster
No, just ONE friend of mine...though if you werr to show up it would be two
Sounds messy
Yeah it may be too messy for you...
though if you wanna be awesome you can show up
Traffic dude!
Well the offer still stands despite the traffic
Well (not as intoxicated) hope traffic lightened up and you got home
Oh I walked home. I just try not to get on the highway in rush hour
Ah I see. So where do you work?
Downtown mpls
Ah descriptive
At Medfinance. Is that better?
I get it, you don't know me, I don't know you
Well, I'm sorry if I have made you feel pressured. I didn't mean anything by it. I know I can be intense and I'm sorry.
Thanks for the apology.
I'll leave you alone.
You're getting emo
Perhaps, but I think it is more realizing how creepy I have been
